title: Help me find the artist for this Kled poster

embed.description: Post with 1 votes and 1 views. Shared by MarianaMagro. MISSING: Pride of Noxus

body:
Hello guys,
Help me find the artist that made this poster for Kled's announcement!

replies.body: I don't rightly remember, but I think either Dan Nortan did it or he would would know.
Might try sending in a support ticket to see if they can ask around.
It was me Dan Norton! Haha... I'm sorry or you're welcome in advance
Now, that's something that I want to frame for my brother
